        "paragraph_index": 0,
        "text": "**The standard electrode potential of Cu²⁺/Cu⁰ is not available in the NIST SRD-46 database.**\n\nSRD-46 is dedicated to **stability constants** (log β, log K) and **pKₐ values** for metal–ligand equilibria in solution. It does not store standard electrode (reduction) potentials. A search of the database's citation records, stability measurements, and table schemas confirmed that no E° data are present.",
